  <notes>Spec FR-6 AC-6a-d (lines 137-140); FR-10 AC-10 (line 152); FR-11 AC-11 (line 155). Hint: use `Moq` (existing test project dep) for ILogger verification — `_loggerMock.Verify(l =&gt; l.Log(LogLevel.Warning, ...), Times.Once)`. Hint: byte-length test should use UTF-8 encoding (System.Text.Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount). Hint: viaMatter-omission test verifies omission semantics chosen in task 020 (omit vs null) — if task 020 chose null, adjust assertion accordingly and document.</notes>

